### HabitForge API Examples

# Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Authentication

### Get Google OAuth2 Login URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/google/login

### After OAuth2 redirect, you'll receive JWT in response
# Use this token for subsequent requests

### 2. Habit Management

### Create a new habit
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Morning Exercise",
  "description": "30 minutes of cardio workout",
  "category": "FITNESS",
  "frequency": "DAILY"
}

### Get all habits (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits?page=0&size=10&sortBy=createdAt&sortDir=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all habits (no pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get specific habit
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update habit
PUT {{baseUrl}}/habits/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Morning Exercise (Updated)",
  "description": "45 minutes of cardio and strength training",
  "category": "FITNESS",
  "frequency": "DAILY"
}

### Delete habit
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/habits/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get habits by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/category/FITNESS
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Habit Logging

### Create/update habit log (mark as complete)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habit-log
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "habitId": 1,
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "status": true
}

### Create/update habit log (mark as incomplete)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habit-log
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "habitId": 1,
  "date": "2024-01-16",
  "status": false
}

### Get logs for specific habit
GET {{baseUrl}}/habit-log/habit/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get logs for date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/habit-log/date-range?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get logs for specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/habit-log/date/2024-01-15
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get today's habit logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/habit-log/today
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get today's stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/habit-log/stats/today
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Reports

### Get weekly report
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/weekly
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get monthly report
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get custom date range report
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/custom?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Progress & Analytics

### Get user progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get category stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/progress/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Refresh user progress
POST {{baseUrl}}/progress/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Error Examples

### Invalid habit ID (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits/999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Missing authorization (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/habits

### Invalid data (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habits
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "category": null,
  "frequency": "DAILY"
}

### Duplicate habit log (409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/habit-log
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "habitId": 1,
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "status": true
}
